      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[NOURISH CAFE WHOLEFOODS PIZZERIA & BAKERY - UNGASAN]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7AyY2LakYstfLi2VxnaaPjSscUe7iKpRT8svlKvRnGS0wGsj0KlnXAO2kUPjICDFhwYqN6ss2U9c2HQVEdLuBhNeqeUCZqVyI94d8-XmCITVC8oMA4gmFv9ywdDIPUXi6BWtYESPLErT4PjLVOJzxvmasvaGnvv6dukAbCfjYcDa6UmxcO2Sa-kke5N-TuKyCPZHGOkCOym-TWAIFlQZ2zluLnBZ9s5Gz6Ktm3rD9kJsE8DkCt2PTtjmQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>美味、有機、本地採購的食材，Nourish正是如此：它用營養豐富的食物、冷壓果汁、健康沙拉和超級食物碗來滋養您的胃。這家全天候咖啡館和比奇圖薩餐廳在Bukit地區有兩個地點；一個位於烏加森，另一個位於Bingin，後者附設有自己的美食全食店。你知道，這些人對高品質、滿足靈魂的食材著迷，盡可能使用和創造有機、本地採購的產品。試試Smashed Avo Stack、Green Bowl和Vegan Morning Glory，再從商店採購所有您最喜愛的營養零食和好吃的東西，你就會明白我們的意思了。]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7AyY2LakYstfLi2VxnaaPjSscUe7iKpRT8svlKvRnGS0wGsj0KlnXAO2kUPjICDFhwYqN6ss2U9c2HQVEdLuBhNeqeUCZqVyI94d8-XmCITVC8oMA4gmFv9ywdDIPUXi6BWtYESPLErT4PjLVOJzxvmasvaGnvv6dukAbCfjYcDa6UmxcO2Sa-kke5N-TuKyCPZHGOkCOym-TWAIFlQZ2zluLnBZ9s5Gz6Ktm3rD9kJsE8DkCt2PTtjmQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
