      <Placemark>
        <name>Bali Buda Bukit</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4kI_Wvy6ZAGzZ8DHe7uMuB6dNP4o4du7osWcWZQt6E3rnvcbJUEU3fugFmfvcWMSoVnvqsbPbGHQnijMth1eQXZx0bPTDhAbK7PIkFQYwlGea864DYNj4qA_erEt_V-CCZygbglO5id5tdiwnRFa63LUzqSIIcyvmRWf9ndED97OwUvdg34N8xvbl5rEP2E5rmb2N8OdeqESmx_GChyOnLjfFa7KL2HYnqj06AfaE2ESDKxpvA9FCw8Vw?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Bali Buda是巴厘島的本地有機餐廳兼雜貨店，擁有豐富的新鮮產品和食材。這個擁有25年歷史的巴厘島機構不提供Wi-Fi，提供一系列生素食菜肴、大沙拉碗、濃郁的湯和無基因改造的豆腐，所有這些都在一個家庭式的咖啡廳環境中。這個島嶼標誌如此受歡迎，它的分店遍及Canggu、Kerobokan、Renon、Batbulan和烏布。]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4kI_Wvy6ZAGzZ8DHe7uMuB6dNP4o4du7osWcWZQt6E3rnvcbJUEU3fugFmfvcWMSoVnvqsbPbGHQnijMth1eQXZx0bPTDhAbK7PIkFQYwlGea864DYNj4qA_erEt_V-CCZygbglO5id5tdiwnRFa63LUzqSIIcyvmRWf9ndED97OwUvdg34N8xvbl5rEP2E5rmb2N8OdeqESmx_GChyOnLjfFa7KL2HYnqj06AfaE2ESDKxpvA9FCw8Vw?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
