      <Placemark>
        <name>Gooseberry Restaurant</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6QyFHoKcVvmBeHfP47KVAxWrvoQiV_Pgy1l_cg4hjQOTNPe0S_ImdD-f-BZO9pCbT-2lbxJeFcVlRIoLh8AacOKVSQiMPc5gAmWF-MWM0C-kZSO2dU8Yvol32Z29MqDHi2sITi0nZtAHOtNWZPFUi_miEcmZTImovSZoRZ03B5gvO5NSgnS9c9HN3Ua4bagdng13pv5s1D5p1JOLmjvm7tthyQL3SQGhqJ_G-R9sgJ_ErLOTzDSHJJVuc?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>隱藏在Bingin Beach上方的Gooseberry Restaurant咖啡館是一個現代美食的熱帶綠洲，配有空調室內和陽光灑落的游泳池，供您在早午餐後享受一下泳池。品嚐咖啡館的早午餐招牌菜（哈羅，平滑果昔碗，三文魚和酪梨多士），然後在晚餐時全力以赴，享受木火爐烹製的乾式熟成頂級牛排烤製而成的美食。]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6QyFHoKcVvmBeHfP47KVAxWrvoQiV_Pgy1l_cg4hjQOTNPe0S_ImdD-f-BZO9pCbT-2lbxJeFcVlRIoLh8AacOKVSQiMPc5gAmWF-MWM0C-kZSO2dU8Yvol32Z29MqDHi2sITi0nZtAHOtNWZPFUi_miEcmZTImovSZoRZ03B5gvO5NSgnS9c9HN3Ua4bagdng13pv5s1D5p1JOLmjvm7tthyQL3SQGhqJ_G-R9sgJ_ErLOTzDSHJJVuc?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
