        <name>Morabito Restaurant</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4h2VvV27nnMuaZk_di4I3cdo0IljrwG2VIOgYX_0MJ3UpNoMXlu8A4QV3aETNm9ZsKSIsLTpDaLfvpOH0BW-waBHOnOH9fugFHImGFriGdJkXEsqdX1T8GR-76hsYJna5n-ftb-xYGaxp_mIcsbIxxSh0yjY8Mh_pr4rzcYDssW0vdIgxTEBSMLvP1C6-ndsL9rGGE9-nP5uVBnqA3xbakuCy-bfgUnP_CmZ3uDjlnp-TRRF-OvkAAqnw?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>像極了聖托里尼島的餐廳]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4h2VvV27nnMuaZk_di4I3cdo0IljrwG2VIOgYX_0MJ3UpNoMXlu8A4QV3aETNm9ZsKSIsLTpDaLfvpOH0BW-waBHOnOH9fugFHImGFriGdJkXEsqdX1T8GR-76hsYJna5n-ftb-xYGaxp_mIcsbIxxSh0yjY8Mh_pr4rzcYDssW0vdIgxTEBSMLvP1C6-ndsL9rGGE9-nP5uVBnqA3xbakuCy-bfgUnP_CmZ3uDjlnp-TRRF-OvkAAqnw?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
