      <Placemark>
        <name>Tsune Uluwatu by Wonderspace</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7cLdHdwXC0RXBF_BGqAsKe1a5f6I7fWn5-IbsZMTvr2KmIgPFQ102SBuQgGwedHAnxZTyhTny5zSMh_CxDc32yvOJA2-bEn5juJ36tIzefXHIHtZQFXLJtbUA6-V1Dlhz7A1VPFCTHNy01-hbsnthORKAT5qsCr5QjxyIZy1gEI_NlvPTMF5WD0DrwbvNm3qcR7ahzThBS2TSb-feR7A6KxU9_F51jzXFM5Jx5L8v_kIyD-lbrpc1cjjI?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>這裡有八折優惠券：https://gobaligo.id/go/uluwatu-guide]]></description>
