        <name>Rockfish at The Uluwatu</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6twqRlY04aD4Wcpgh0wRDgebk_Up7lonlhmwuqRW72h6PZN0CIz44z7h2qiLwqa1dxoXku_SNq0OSr0wdczqg_pZ8gmcq__Rg9CJ4olc6JQZB7D-4E0QMwszQE5Btuv2aUR-jo7w6iyeUCMxxqDEcfZsg6lMZAd6YUJgGOMtyInegFYknMU17BUV0DxWnrEYzQwlj7yy2RiQgMa2EO8oyS-Hkag2jRBl1iD0sr4PsIkqTBHIeuk7ucPe8?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>rockfish 洞穴餐廳（不是很貴的那家），沒有低消，可以只喝飲料 【羅惠郡提供】]]></description>
